title: Bohemian Raw Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Western, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe offering vegan choices such as raw cakes, desserts, smoothies, boho bowls, balls and acai bowls. Coconut latte and golden latte are dairy-free. Savory take away lunches are mostly raw, vegan; wraps contain gluten. Its other location at Victoria Point location is pure veg.
streetAddress: Abell Point Marina, South Village, Shop 1A Shingley Dr, Airlie Beach
